{"tid":645983,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[盃賽最頂上一戰]17-18 LIHKG香港女神總會盃決賽--文詠珊 對 李佳芯","createTime":"2018-04-28T16:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T20:03:11.000Z","uid":92376,"like":131,"dislike":200,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dec87e927cd5641f9d7189275dbbb8f08a3c11a3","tid":645983,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"以下為馬上舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可直接以正負評功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(冠)文詠珊vs李佳芯(超)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG香港女神總會盃決賽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名(非聯賽者則以非聯表示)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-4-29 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/sym9mKC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fsym9mKC.png&h=7fc067ad&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Dnsh6ug.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDnsh6ug.png&h=fe8d1f0e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(冠1)文詠珊vs李佳芯(超2)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以正負評功能投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽決賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"84b80f02b8dabc597600d4b3c9d53aec2d09816f","tid":645983,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"文詠珊晉級過程:<br />\n第一圈 54-2 杜如風(乙組)<br />\n第二圈 27-9 孫慧雪(冠聯)<br />\n第三圈 31-9 陳嘉寶(冠聯)<br />\n十六強 94-39 陳靜(非聯)<br />\n八強 兩回合56-34 劉穎鏇(甲組)<br />\n四強 兩回合184-119 苟芸慧(超聯)<br />\n<br />\n李佳芯晉級過程:<br />\n第三圈 27-9 陳瀅(超聯)<br />\n十六強 122-14 朱智賢(乙組)<br />\n八強 兩回合133-37 沈卓盈(冠聯)<br />\n四強 兩回合178-150 朱千雪(超聯)"},{"pid":"178f2bfe50769e2dac693272647965712b2759cd","tid":645983,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab50bf0767bcc3f8288296c725e3cc291e74041f","tid":645983,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:11:41.000Z","msg":"文詠珊開賽十分鐘暫時稍稍領先"},{"pid":"8774c10717d8d9cfdea8f276c736b85790b9a675","tid":645983,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:11:52.000Z","msg":"比分8-6"},{"pid":"3958db9d0cc5897656d4fefdbc649b83f028c987","tid":645983,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:12:19.000Z","msg":"8-7"},{"pid":"19e9137f13a10b669644ab886f60c61a0d8a20bd","tid":645983,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:14:30.000Z","msg":"賽事資訊：<br />\n來季文詠珊將會從冠聯升班超聯<br />\n因為佢已經提早鎖定左升班資格<br />\n<br />\n而李佳芯喺聯賽就仲有少少機會反先到朱千雪，但真係好微"},{"pid":"4065148e37f9d82ab923bde15975fa30e4b52b26","tid":645983,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"11-8"},{"pid":"f142a52133dc0b7f84a9e124c3c40649af246405","tid":645983,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"14-10"},{"pid":"6853fb31f7fb7235a6c6e4c45fd89d99c6c5922c","tid":645983,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"